quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,The Multus Gracious
  55,2,Ludimagister Quran
  55,3,Creator human beings
  55,4,He taught them quam distinguish
  55,5,sun moon perfectly calculated
  55,6,stars trees prostrate
  55,7,He constructed caelum established juris
  55,8,Vos non transgress juris
  55,9,Vos establish justice non violate juris
  55,10,He created terra totus creatures
  55,11,In it ibi est fruits datum palms their hanging fruit
  55,12,Alias grains ac spices
  55,13,(O humans jinns) de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny
  55,14,He created human aetatis clay figulus clay
  55,15,Ac created jinns ex blazing fire
  55,16,(O humans jinns) de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny
  55,17,Dominus de 2 easts 2 wests
  55,18,Quae de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny
  55,19,He separates 2 seas ubi they meet
  55,20,barrier locus them prevent them ex transgressing
  55,21,Quae de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny
  55,22,Out de ambo them vos get pearls ac coral
  55,23,Quae de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny
  55,24,He dedit vos ships ut roam sea like flags
  55,25,Quae de tuus Dominus marvels vos deny